00:16:09,320 --> 00:16:13,320
Even though there are fewer Six Flags parks today than there were 20 years ago, this continuous

248
00:16:13,320 --> 00:16:18,460
differentiation on spectacle and the company's unmatched scale have kept Six Flags up as

249
00:16:18,460 --> 00:16:21,460
a cheaper alternative to Disney and Universal.

250
00:16:21,460 --> 00:16:25,100
Yet the construction and design costs of these rides are not trivial, and the payback

