00:16:25,100 --> 00:16:31,180
periods are lengthy, as Six Flags invests over $100 million every year in capital expenditures.

252
00:16:31,180 --> 00:16:37,260
$100 million annually is roughly 9 to 10% of Six Flags gross revenue, but 30 to 50%

253
00:16:37,260 --> 00:16:41,480
of operating income, which is ultimately what matters since that's the cash you actually

