00:16:55,480 --> 00:16:59,700
In an attempt to level the playing field with Disney and Universal, Six Flags has branded

258
00:16:59,700 --> 00:17:04,980
its rides and parks over the decades with iconic fictional characters like Bugs Bunny,

259
00:17:04,980 --> 00:17:11,300
Batman, Tweety Bird, Superman, and the Flintstones, a healthy mix of idolized superheroes and

