00:18:00,180 --> 00:18:04,460
followed by food and merchandise sales inside the park, and then finally sponsorships and

272
00:18:04,460 --> 00:18:05,900
licensing.

273
00:18:05,900 --> 00:18:11,300
Revenue has been on a steady climb at 4% growth year over year for Six Flags, going from $880

