00:18:20,980 --> 00:18:26,140
In the early 2000s, the average Six Flags grows between $20 to $30 million every year.

277
00:18:26,140 --> 00:18:31,700
In the 2010s before the pandemic, the average Six Flags park grows between $50 to $60 million

278
00:18:31,700 --> 00:18:33,020
every year.

